proc CoppiaEK6(jmp A, jmp B)
"USAGE:    CoppiaEK(A,B); A list, B list
RETURN:   list: L
NOTE:     At the end the monomials involved by EK.
EXAMPLE:  example CoppiaEK6; shows an example"
{
